Fake Job Detection Using Machine Learning
ğŸ“– Description

A short overview of your project:

This project aims to detect fake job postings using machine learning techniques. It analyzes job descriptions and other metadata to identify fraudulent listings, helping users avoid scams in online job markets.

ğŸš€ Features

Predicts whether a job posting is fake or real

Uses NLP (Natural Language Processing) for text analysis

User-friendly web interface (Flask/Streamlit)

Trained on a labeled dataset of job postings

