ğŸ“Š Dataset

You can mention your dataset:

The dataset used for training and testing is from Kaggle Fake Job Posting Dataset
.

ğŸ§  Model Training

Briefly describe your ML model:

The text data is vectorized using TF-IDF and trained using a Logistic Regression classifier. The model achieves around 96% accuracy on the test set.

ğŸ’» Usage

Explain how users can interact with your app:

Enter a job description in the input box and click Predict. The app will output whether the job posting is Real or Fake.

